    <item>
      <title>Updated version for eZ publish 4.x</title>
      <link>http://projects.ez.no/akismet/forum/general/updated_version_for_ez_publish_4_x</link>
      <description>Based on this extension we released an updated version for eZ publish 4.x:&#13;
&#13;
The version for 4.x differs from the version by Kristof:&#13;
- It is not integrated with the ez approval workflow, but can of course be combined with the approval workflow;&#13;
- It does not require custom information extrator php classes, but can be configured in the configuration file;&#13;
- It uses the PHP5 version of the Akismet class developed by Bret Kuhns, improving performance;&#13;
- The name of the module view 'akismet/submit' has been changed to 'akismet/reportspam';&#13;
&#13;
It is available at:&#13;
http://code.google.com/p/ezakismet/</description>
      <author>community@ez.no (S V)</author>
      <guid>http://projects.ez.no/akismet/forum/general/updated_version_for_ez_publish_4_x</guid>
